 Minuten bei Ihnen, egal ob in Wien, Niederösterreich oder dem Burgenland.</p> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-59e6f67 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="59e6f67" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-977110c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="977110c" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3413fec elementor-position-inline-start elementor-view-default elementor-mobile-position-block-start elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box" data-id="3413fec" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="icon-box.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <div class="elementor-icon-box-wrapper"> <div class="elementor-icon-box-icon"> <span class="elementor-icon"> <svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-home" viewbox="0 0 576 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M280.37 148.26L96 300.11V464a16 16 0 0 0 16 16l112.06-.29a16 16 0 0 0 15.92-16V368a16 16 0 0 1 16-16h64a16 16 0 0 1 16 16v95.64a16 16 0 0 0 16 16.05L464 480a16 16 0 0 0 16-16V300L295.67 148.26a12.19 12.19 0 0 0-15.3 0zM571.6 251.47L488 182.56V44.05a12 12 0 0 0-12-12h-56a12 12 0 0 0-12 12v72.61L318.47 43a48 48 0 0 0-61 0L4.34 251.47a12 12 0 0 0-1.6 16.9l25.5 31A12 12 0 0 0 45.15 301l235.22-193.74a12.19 12.19 0 0 1 15.3 0L530.9 301a12 12 0 0 0 16.9-1.6l25.5-31a12 12 0 0 0-1.7-16.93z"></path></svg> </span> </div> <div class="elementor-icon-box-content"> <h3 class="elementor-icon-box-title"> <span> Für Privathaushalte </span> </h3> <p class="elementor-icon-box-description"> Unser Thermen-Notdienst ist 24 Stunden am Tag, 7 Tage die Woche in Wien, Niederösterreich und dem Burgenland verfügbar. Wir sind in nur 40 Minuten bei Ihnen. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9056d0a elementor-position-inline-start elementor-view-default elementor-mobile-position-block